The Other Side of Never: Dark Tales from the World of Peter and Wendy

Publisher Description

Dark tales inspired by J. M. Barrie's classic stories of Neverland, Captain Hook, Tinkerbell, and of course Peter Pan, from some the masters of science-fiction, horror and fantasy including A. C. Wise...
